flowchart TB

    %% ─── Shared foundation ───
    FOUNDATION[Shared Foundation<br/>methodology &middot; accelerators &middot; AI-native delivery]

    %% ─── The four circles ───
    subgraph CIRCLES [The four practice circles]
        direction LR
        PLAT[Platform Circle<br/>application development<br/>delivery models<br/>strategy &middot; value props]
        ENT[Enterprise Circle<br/>Salesforce &middot; MuleSoft<br/>Kafka &middot; data platforms]
        COTS[COTS Circle<br/>Power BI &middot; Tableau<br/>Power Automate &middot; Fabric]
        LEG[Legacy Modernization<br/>knowledge extraction<br/>strangler-fig &middot; rewrite]
