    FOUNDATION --> LEG

    PLAT  --- CROSS
    ENT   --- CROSS
    COTS  --- CROSS
    LEG   --- CROSS

    PLAT --> ENG
    ENT  --> ENG
    COTS --> ENG
    LEG  --> ENG

